name: state-of-hawaii-department-of-health-clean-water-branch-state-wide-water-quality-sampling-datas
notes: The Monitoring Section of the State of Hawaii, Department of Health, Clean Water Branch collects water quality data at over 300 coastal locations state-wide using well-established instruments and methodologies. This dataset spans 1973-1998. This dataset replaces NODC Accession 9800067 (Original STORET output format) with the new CSV format. This new set also adds 1/1/1998-12/31/1998.
